I'm assuming that since DrillBit is back at base, Robo had Killfest go back too.

::Killfest/Scyther/Incarcinator::

Killfest recieves the transmission from Shivah, walking off instantly to the conference room. He enters, looking around. "What's the situation?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Scyther and Incarcinator peer around, trying to figure out if they were still in the shuttle or if they (and EndBringer and Demise) were at the BlackFortress by now (please tell me, Airly. I have no clue).
